description:
Danny welcomes Cody Rhodes and Brandi Rhodes from the new AEW (All Elite Wrestling). They discuss Cody's legendary father, Dusty Rhodes, the launch of AEW, WWE, Brandi's time on WAGS: Atlanta and being a black female executive in a male-dominated industry, and SO much more.


Cody & Brandi Rhodes Interview: 2:18ish
